Cell["\<\
some nodes appear to be adjacent, others next-to-adjacent, but that is an \
artifact of the diagram (or better: of the way we tend to look at the \
diagram, our eye following the perimeter). In fact, the nodal \
interrelationships are symmetric, identical: every node is adjacent to every \
other. So the claim\
\>", "Text",
